title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, Medical Plants
description: Imports Intra Eu - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, Medical Plants in the United Kingdom decreased to 68.14 GBP Million in September from 70.08 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, in the United Kingdom averaged 286.21 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 44904.10 GBP Million in March of 2015 and a record low of 5.21 GBP Million in June of 2002. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Frui.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
